
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>AmicBridge – Structured Lending, Borrowing & Investing</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="AmicBridge is a structured private network where people lend, borrow and invest with written agreements, clear expectations and shared profit."
    />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f3f4f6;
        --white: #ffffff;
        --primary: #1d4ed8;
        --primary-dark: #1e3a8a;
        --border: #d1d5db;
        --text-main: #111827;
        --text-muted: #6b7280;
        --success-bg: #ecfdf3;
        --success-border: #bbf7d0;
        --success-text: #166534;
        --warn-bg: #fff7ed;
        --warn-border: #fed7aa;
        --warn-text: #9a3412;
      }

      * { box-sizing: border-box; }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Arial, sans-serif;
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text-main);
      }

      a { color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; }
      a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

      header {
        background: var(--white);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 14px 24px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .brand-block { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }

      .logo {
        font-weight: 800;
        font-size: 20px;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .logo span { color: var(--primary-dark); }

      .top-meta {
        font-size: 11px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      nav {
        display: flex;
        gap: 18px;
        font-size: 14px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      nav a { color: var(--text-main); font-weight: 500; }

      .container {
        max-width: 960px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 28px 16px 52px;
      }

      .hero {
        margin-top: 24px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 3fr) minmax(0, 2fr);
        gap: 28px;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .trust-tag {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        padding: 4px 10px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #e0f2fe;
        color: #0369a1;
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .hero h1 { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 32px; }
      .hero-subtitle { margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 520px; }

      .hero-cta { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; }

      .btn-primary {
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 9px 16px;
        border: 1px solid var(--primary-dark);
        background: var(--primary-dark);
        color: #fff;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .btn-secondary {
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 9px 16px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        background: var(--white);
        color: var(--text-main);
        cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .hero-card {
        background: var(--white);
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 14px 16px;
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      .hero-card h3 { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 15px; }

      .hero-pill-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; }

      .hero-pill {
        padding: 4px 9px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        background: #f9fafb;
        font-size: 11px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      h2.section-title { font-size: 20px; margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
      .section-sub { margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); }

      .grid-3 {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .card {
        background: var(--white);
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 14px 16px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .card h3 { margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 15px; }
      .card p { margin: 0; color: var(--text-muted); }

      .list {
        margin: 6px 0 0;
        padding-left: 18px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      .list li { margin-bottom: 3px; }

      .two-col {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 3fr) minmax(0, 2fr);
        gap: 18px;
      }

      .badge-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-top: 8px; }

      .badge {
        font-size: 11px;
        padding: 4px 10px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: var(--success-bg);
        border: 1px solid var(--success-border);
        color: var(--success-text);
      }

      .contact-card {
        background: var(--white);
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 14px 16px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .steps {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .step { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); }
      .step strong { display: block; color: var(--text-main); margin-bottom: 2px; }

      /* Offer highlight */
      .offer-card {
        border: 1px solid var(--warn-border);
        background: var(--warn-bg);
      }
      .offer-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 12px;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }
      .offer-box {
        background: var(--white);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 10px 12px;
        font-size: 13px;
      }
      .offer-label {
        font-size: 11px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin-bottom: 2px;
      }
      .offer-value {
        font-weight: 800;
        font-size: 16px;
        color: var(--text-main);
      }
      .offer-note {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: var(--warn-text);
        margin-top: 10px;
        line-height: 1.35;
      }

      footer {
        font-size: 11px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background: var(--white);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        header { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 6px; }
        .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .grid-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .offer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: 26px; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="brand-block">
        <div class="logo">AMIC<span>BRIDGE</span></div>
        <div class="top-meta">
          Based in Norway · Private lending & investing network
        </div>
      </div>

      <nav>
        <a href="#offer">Current offer</a>
        <a href="#how">How it works</a>
        <a href="#who">Who it is for</a>
        <a href="#trust">Trust & agreements</a>
        <a href="#currency">Currency</a>
        <a href="#stablecoin">Stablecoin</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
      <section class="hero">
        <div>
          <div class="trust-tag"><span>✔</span> TRUST BEFORE MONEY</div>

          <h1>Structured lending, borrowing and investing between people.</h1>

          <p class="hero-subtitle">
            AmicBridge is a private network where people help each other with
            capital – always with written agreements, clear expectations and
            realistic profit sharing.
          </p>

          <div class="hero-cta">
            <a href="#contact"><button class="btn-primary">Contact CEO</button></a>
            <a href="#how"><button class="btn-secondary">Learn how it works</button></a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="hero-card">
          <h3>AmicBridge in one look</h3>
          <div class="hero-pill-row">
            <span class="hero-pill">Written agreements</span>
            <span class="hero-pill">Clear expectations</span>
            <span class="hero-pill">No hidden fees</span>
            <span class="hero-pill">Human-to-human network</span>
            <span class="hero-pill">Current offer: 45,000 → 52,000 (4 weeks)</span>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </section>

      <!-- NEW: Current offer -->
      <section id="offer">
        <h2 class="section-title">Current offer</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">A fixed, written agreement offer available in the network.</p>

        <div class="card offer-card">
          <h3>Offer terms (example agreement)</h3>
          <p class="section-sub" style="margin-bottom:0;">
            AmicBridge can lend out <strong>45,000</strong> and receive <strong>52,000</strong> back in <strong>4 weeks</strong>
            — only with a written agreement and clear responsibilities.
          </p>

          <div class="offer-grid">
            <div class="offer-box">
              <div class="offer-label">Amount lent</div>
              <div class="offer-value">45,000</div>
            </div>
            <div class="offer-box">
              <div class="offer-label">Amount returned</div>
              <div class="offer-value">52,000</div>
            </div>
            <div class="offer-box">
              <div class="offer-label">Timeframe</div>
              <div class="offer-value">4 weeks</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="offer-note">
            Note: This is a private-network offer and requires verification, identity checks where needed,
            and a signed written agreement describing currency, dates, and responsibilities.
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="how">
        <h2 class="section-title">How it works</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">Clarity, structure and simplicity.</p>

        <div class="grid-3">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>1. Lend</h3>
            <p>Private lenders provide capital under written terms.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>2. Borrow</h3>
            <p>Borrowers receive funding with a clear agreement.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>3. Share profit</h3>
            <p>Success leads to structured profit sharing.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="who">
        <h2 class="section-title">Who AmicBridge is for</h2>

        <div class="grid-3">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Private lenders</h3>
            <p>Individuals who want professional structure.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Projects & builders</h3>
            <p>People with concrete plans that need funding.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Long-term investors</h3>
            <p>Those who prefer agreements over hype.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="trust">
        <h2 class="section-title">Trust & agreements</h2>

        <div class="two-col">
          <div>
            <p class="section-sub">
              The principle is simple: <strong>Trust before money. Agreement before action.</strong>
            </p>

            <div class="card">
              <h3>Written agreements on every deal</h3>
              <ul class="list">
                <li>Loan agreements</li>
                <li>Investment & profit-sharing agreements</li>
                <li>Clear amounts, timelines and responsibilities</li>
              </ul>

              <div class="badge-row">
                <span class="badge">Plain language terms</span>
                <span class="badge">Professional structure</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="currency">
        <h2 class="section-title">Currency choice</h2>

        <div class="card">
          <p class="section-sub">
            Currency is chosen by both parties and written into the agreement.
            We can help with transferring funds via bank or crypto (small and large amounts),
            depending on the agreed setup.
          </p>

          <ul class="list">
            <li>Crypto</li>
            <li>Stablecoins</li>
            <li>NOK · SEK · EUR · USD</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="stablecoin">
        <h2 class="section-title">Stablecoin option</h2>

        <div class="card">
          <p class="section-sub">
            Stablecoins provide fast and predictable transfers when both sides agree.
          </p>

          <ul class="list">
            <li>Fast settlement</li>
            <li>Predictable transfer value</li>
            <li>Useful when bank transfers are slow</li>
            <li>Always linked to a written agreement</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="start">
        <h2 class="section-title">How to get started</h2>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="steps">
            <div class="step">
              <strong>1. Send an email</strong>
              Say if you want to lend, borrow or invest.
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <strong>2. Discuss</strong>
              Terms, expectations and currency are discussed.
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <strong>3. Agreement</strong>
              A written agreement is created and signed.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="contact">
        <h2 class="section-title">Contact</h2>

        <div class="two-col">
          <div class="contact-card">
            <h3>Direct contact</h3>
            <p>CEO: <strong>Ernest</strong></p>

            <p style="font-size:14px;">
              phone: 92928373
              Email:
              <a href="mailto:amicbridgecontact@gmail.com">amicbridgecontact@gmail.com</a>
            </p>

            <p class="section-sub">
              Write briefly who you are and whether you want to lend, borrow or invest.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>Helpful details</h3>
            <ul class="list">
              <li>Your role</li>
              <li>Approximate amount</li>
              <li>Preferred currency</li>
              <li>Short description</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <footer>
      <span>© <span id="year"></span> AmicBridge · Trust Before Money</span>
      <span>Private financial network.</span>
    </footer>

    <script>
      // Current year in plain HTML
      document.getElementById("year").textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
